      </tr>
      <tr style="height:100%;"> 
       <td class="wizardStep"> <p> Welcome to the Mississippi Public Service Commission Online Utility Complaint form. This form allows you to register a&nbsp; complaint related to a utility service provider.&nbsp; Before you begin, be sure you have the following information:</p> 
        <ul> 
         <li>Your address and contact information</li> 
         <li>The name of the utility company, and the county in which your service is provided</li> 
         <li>Your account number with the utility company.</li> 
        </ul> <p> If you are not filing a utility complaint, choose one of the following to be directed to the appropriate form: </p> 
        <ul> 
         <li><a href="https://www.psc.state.ms.us/nocall/nocall.html">I would like to file a telemarketer complaint.</a></li> 
         <li><a href="http://www.psc.state.ms.us/mpsc/ztg/zapthegap.html">I would like to report poor mobile phone coverage.</a></li> 
         <li><a href="http://www.psc.state.ms.us/mpsc/ztg/zapthegap.html">I would like to report lack of high speed Internet service.</a></li> 
         <li><a href="http://www.psc.state.ms.us">Return me to the Public Service Commission Website</a>.</li> 
        </ul> <p> If you are ready to begin, click 'Next' below.</p> </td> 
      </tr>
